com.koloboke.collect.map.hash

Interface HashObjIntMap<K>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Container, HashContainer, Map<K,Integer>, ObjIntMap<K>

    public interface HashObjIntMap<K>
extends ObjIntMap<K>, HashContainer
    An interface for ObjIntMaps, based on hash tables.

    This interface doesn't carry own specific behaviour, just combines it's superinterfaces.

    Looking for a way to instantiate a HashObjIntMap? See static factory methods in HashObjIntMaps class.

    See Also:
    HashObjIntMapFactory, HashObjIntMaps, @KolobokeMap
